f the\nflux-reduction factor in a statistically limited result, the possibility of\nobserving hadronic beams is undermined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2011 08:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
